Package com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqscscripts Description

This is the root package of the MQSC Scripts Plugin. THe MQSC Scripts Plugin is responsible for all of the UI components of MS0S. It implements an MQExplorer plugin, per the documentation here
